            "title": "Mesquite bugs, other insects, and a bat in the diet of pallid bats in southeastern Arizona",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Nicholas J.",
                    "lastName": "Czaplewski"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
